{"tid":1929094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍戰機今夜一度飛近台灣的防空識別區","createTime":"2020-03-16T18:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T18:40:28.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e879d1e2c5bafdaac58bb6e7fe794c5a3a494d0b","tid":1929094,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"在台北，國防部表示，解放軍派出多架戰機，包括空警500、殲11戰機，昨晚7時在台灣西南方海域，執行夜間飛行訓練，期間曾接近台灣防空識別區，台灣出動戰機升空監控，對解放軍戰機進行廣播後，解放軍戰機之後飛離台灣的防空識別區，期間全程掌握動向。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的國防部表示，解放軍戰機以往都是在日間飛近，今次是首度在夜間飛到台灣附近，形容情況罕見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917104579144ed7b7598b3e99291860888e86606","tid":1929094,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514880-20200317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514880-20200317.htm&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=2fb3518d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514880-20200317.htm&h=2583dba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514880-20200317.htm</a>"},{"pid":"145c0c0cc4c984ae9c9ce93c806df0219d4d12cf","tid":1929094,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:07:25.000Z","msg":"點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />